Name: cobalt_funding_later_content
clcommon__Content__c:
You have decided to fund your account(s) later; please read the following to determine which path makes the most sense for your business:

If you have an existing business account with us, feel free to fund your account(s) from your existing account in online banking.

If you would like to fund via check, please send a check to our offices at $state(cobaltCustomSettingsPanel).attr(baodev__Office_Address__c);.

If you would like to review your application, here is your application ID for future reference: $global.attr(appNumber);

Remember, you can always come back to look at your application status at any point in time.

Thank you again for your interest in Thrive Financial!

You may now close this tab.
